# Volunteering vocabulary

## Namespaces
### Ontology Base URI
prefix :                <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/>

### Core W3C ontologies (OWL 2 reserved vocabulary)
prefix rdf:             <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
prefix rdfs:            <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
prefix owl:             <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
prefix xsd:             <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

### Other namespaces used
prefix dc:              <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
prefix skos:            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
prefix time:            <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
prefix vcard:           <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>
prefix vann:            <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/>


## Ontology
<https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/>
    a owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    dc:issued "2025-11-20"^^xsd:date ;
    vann:preferredNamespacePrefix "volunteering" ;
    vann:preferredNamespaceUri "https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/"^^xsd:anyURI ;
    rdfs:label "Volunteering and Social Action Ontology"@en ;
    rdfs:seeAlso <https://standard.volunteeringdata.io/ontology/> ;
    dc:description "Defines a vocabulary to describe volunteering activities, volunteer-involving organisations and volunteering management systems."@en ;
.


## Datatype Properties
:address
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has address"@en ;
.

:allowsRemoteParticipation
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "allows remote participation"@en ;
.

:applyLink
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has apply link"@en ;
.

:charityNumber
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has charity number"@en ;
.

:description
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf dc:description ;
    rdfs:label "has description"@en ;
.

:latitude
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has latitude"@en ;
.

:longitude
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has longitude"@en ;
.

:name
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has name"@en ;
.

:requiresEmergencyParticipation
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "requires emergency participation"@en ;
.

:title
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has title"@en ;
.

:website
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has website"@en ;
.
